{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-278-linear-combinations-of-semiprimes","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 278: Linijska kombinacija semiprima brojeva","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Neka su dati celobrojni brojevi $1 &#x3C; a_1 &#x3C; a_2 &#x3C; \\ldots &#x3C; a_n$, razmotri linearnu kombinaciju $q_1a_1 + q_2a_2 + \\ldots + q_na_n = b$, koristeći samo celobrojne vrednosti $q_k ≥ 0$.</p>\n<p>Zapamtite da za određeni skup $a_k$, možda nisu sve vrednosti $b$ moguće. Na primer, ako su $a_1 = 5$ i $a_2 = 7$, ne postoji $q_1 \\ge 0$ i $q_2 \\ge 0$ takvo da bi $b$ mogao biti 1, 2, 3, 4, 6, 8, 9, 11, 13, 16, 18 ili 23.</p>\n<p>Zapravo, 23 je najveća moguća vrednost za $b$ kada su $a_1 = 5$ i $a_2 = 7$. Stoga nazivamo $f(5, 7) = 23$. Slično tome, može se pokazati da $f(6, 10, 15)=29$ i $f(14, 22, 77) = 195$.</p>\n<p>Izračunaj $\\sum f(pq,pr,qr)$, gde su $p$, $q$ i $r$ premijni brojevi i $p &#x3C; q &#x3C; r &#x3C; 5000$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4831000cf542c50ff95","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301928,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-278-linear-combinations-of-semiprimes"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function linearCombinationOfSemiprimes() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nlinearCombinationOfSemiprimes();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>linearCombinationOfSemiprimes()</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>1228215747273908500</code>.</p>","testString":"assert